https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Justin-Hawkins-and-Taylor-Hawkins.-CREDIT_-Harry-Herd_Redferns-and-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Justin-Hawkins-and-Taylor-Hawkins.-CREDIT_-Harry-Herd_Redferns-and-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Justin-Hawkins-and-Taylor-Hawkins.-CREDIT_-Harry-Herd_Redferns-and-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Justin-Hawkins-and-Taylor-Hawkins.-CREDIT_-Harry-Herd_Redferns-and-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Justin-Hawkins-and-Taylor-Hawkins.-CREDIT_-Harry-Herd_Redferns-and-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Justin-Hawkins-and-Taylor-Hawkins.-CREDIT_-Harry-Herd_Redferns-and-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Justin-Hawkins-and-Taylor-Hawkins.-CREDIT_-Harry-Herd_Redferns-and-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-darkness">黑暗的</a>主持人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-hawkins">贾斯汀·霍金斯（Justin Hawkins）</a>透露，他对已故<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-hawkins">泰勒·霍金斯（Taylor Hawkins）</a>的致敬音乐会表演感到“石化”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/taylor-hawkins-tribute-concert-wembley-foo-fighters-cover-3306358">阅读更多：泰勒·霍金斯（Taylor Hawkins）致敬音乐会：“一个巨大的他妈的他妈的人的巨大夜晚”</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>与泰勒无关的霍金斯（Hawkins）是伦敦<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">（Foo Fighters）</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-drummer-taylor-hawkins-has-died-3190788">50岁时去世</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/taylor-hawkins-tribute-concert-wembley-foo-fighters-cover-3306358#:~:text=Liam%20Gallagher%20tapped%20into%20the,Pretenders%2C%20all%20bands%20that%20Hawkins">2022年在伦敦和洛杉矶举行的致敬表演</a>的一部分。</p><p>现在，他分享说， <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/taylor-hawkins-tribute-concert-wembley-foo-fighters-cover-3306358">在巨大的演出中表演</a>最初似乎是一项艰巨的任务。在对<a href="https://www.rollingstone.co.uk/music/features/the-last-word-justin-hawkins-interview-darkness-dreams-on-toast-49013/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>英国Rolling Stone</em></a>的新采访中，主持人分享道：“当泰勒去世时，这对我们来说是毁灭性的，因为他是鲁弗斯（泰勒（Daylor），鼓手）的教父。</p><p> “我们在加拿大的路上，这是一个糟糕的时刻，所以我们尽了最大的努力来支持Rufus。</p><p> “但是我也认识泰勒，我们开玩笑说拥有同样的姓氏，甚至有一个人声称自己是我们之间缺少的家庭联系。</p><p> “我接到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-grohl">戴夫·格罗尔（Dave Grohl）</a>的电话，我有点像是在某种程度上被吓呆了，因为他对我来说意义重大，而且危在旦夕。我不想陷入困境。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Foo Fighters Taylor Hawkins Tribute（W/Queen＆Justin Hawkins） - 我们将摇摆您（论坛9/27/22）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/oN-Vuxf-nGU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="我相信一个叫做爱情的东西 - 黑暗 - 泰勒·霍金斯（Taylor Hawkins）致敬音乐会拉动论坛" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Kvd8SLEc-3Q?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他继续说，他花了一些时间为演出做准备，并最终对表演感到满意。他说：“我预订了一家工作室，我为它做好了适当的准备，这与我不同。”</p><p> “我必须做对了，这是非常受欢迎的，我认为那是人们开始对我有所不同的时候。</p><p> “我也与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/acdc">AC/DC</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brian-johnson">布莱恩·约翰逊（Brian Johnson）</a>一起演出，他聊天后给我打了电话，最近我在奖项上看到了他。</p><p> “认为我被认为我是国宝，这让我震惊，但认为我与我的一位实际英雄的名字更加震惊。”</p><p>在音乐会期间，霍金斯（Hawkins）与已故的Foo Fighters鼓手副计划<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-hawkins-the-coattail-riders">The Coattail Riders</a>的成员一起表演了四首歌。</p><p>在洛杉矶的表演中 - 贾斯汀·霍金斯（Justin Hawkins）和弗雷斯（Freese）在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-gang">詹姆斯·甘（James Gang）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-ronson">马克·罗森（Mark Ronson）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/andrew-wyatt">安德鲁·怀亚特（Andrew Wyatt）</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/them-crooked-vultures">他们弯曲的秃鹰</a>之后的表演之后，与格罗尔（Grohl）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wolfgang-van-halen">沃尔夫冈·范·哈伦（Wolfgang Van Halen）</a>一起登台演出，表演了两首范<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/van-halen">·海伦（Van Halen）</a>歌曲。</p><p>与此同时，在伦敦，霍金斯在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queen">皇后</a>区打算<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brian-may-and-roger-taylor-join-foo-fighters-for-queen-set-at-taylor-hawkins-tribute-concert-3303966">在“压力下”发表客串人声</a>，并与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lars-ulrich">拉尔斯·乌尔里希（Lars Ulrich）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brian-johnson">布莱恩·约翰逊（Brian Johnson）</a>一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/metallica-lars-ulrich-ac-dc-brian-johnson-taylor-hawkins-tribute-concert-3303897">发表</a>嘉宾人声，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/acdc">AC/DC</a>命中“ Back in Black in Black&#39;中，邀请了客人。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="巴拿马 - 沃尔夫冈·范·哈伦，贾斯汀·霍金斯和戴夫·格罗尔 - 泰勒·霍金斯致敬音乐会" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VyHc1cNRBcU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在其他新闻中，《黑暗》在星期五（3月28日）发行了他们的最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-darkness-announce-new-album-dreams-on-toast-and-2025-uk-tour-including-wembley-show-with-ash-3794787">“ Dreams On Toast”</a> 。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-stylistics-shania-twain-the-darkness-justin-hawkins-first-album-nearly-two-decades-3824388">霍金斯（Hawkins）在近二十年来的第一张新专辑中锁