" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3850339" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3850339" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Morgan-Wallen.-CREDIT_-John-Shearer_Getty-Images-for-Morgan-Wallens-One-Night-At-A-Time-2024.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Morgan-Wallen.-CREDIT_-John-Shearer_Getty-Images-for-Morgan-Wallens-One-Night-At-A-Time-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Morgan-Wallen.-CREDIT_-John-Shearer_Getty-Images-for-Morgan-Wallens-One-Night-At-A-Time-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Morgan-Wallen.-CREDIT_-John-Shearer_Getty-Images-for-Morgan-Wallens-One-Night-At-A-Time-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Morgan-Wallen.-CREDIT_-John-Shearer_Getty-Images-for-Morgan-Wallens-One-Night-At-A-Time-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Morgan-Wallen.-CREDIT_-John-Shearer_Getty-Images-for-Morgan-Wallens-One-Night-At-A-Time-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Morgan-Wallen.-CREDIT_-John-Shearer_Getty-Images-for-Morgan-Wallens-One-Night-At-A-Time-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3850339" class="wp-caption-text">摩根·沃伦（Morgan Wallen）的一晚2024年的约翰·希勒/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://x.com/JesseSpots/status/1906220992482938919" target="_blank" rel="noopener">另一位用户写道</a>：“该死，您可以从氛围中分辨出&#39;这是一个不好的人。&#39;”。 <a href="https://variety.com/2025/music/news/morgan-wallen-snl-walk-off-gods-country-social-post-1236352063/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">一份<em>综艺</em>报道</a>分享说，接近沃伦（Wallen）的消息人士维持这位歌手在纽约拍摄的演出中度过了愉快的时光，他的出口和Instagram帖子并不意味着对其演员阵容有点。</p><p>瓦伦（Wallen）仍然是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radio-stations-and-playlists-drop-country-star-morgan-wallen-over-use-of-racial-slur-2871551">他在网上浮出水面的种族诽谤，使他仍然是一个有争议的人物镜头</a>，导致他被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radio-stations-and-playlists-drop-country-star-morgan-wallen-over-use-of-racial-slur-2871551">许多广播电台</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallen-dropped-by-big-loud-records-after-using-racial-slur-2872596">他的唱片公司大声</a>响起。</p><p>尽管如此， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallen-sees-surge-album-sales-video-racial-slur-spread-online-2874316">他的专辑“危险”的销售额仍在激增</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallen-maintains-americas-no-1-album-two-weeks-after-racial-slur-video-2880492">，</a>沃伦在Billboard 200专辑排行榜上保持了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallens-dangerous-sets-new-country-album-record-weeks-on-from-racial-slur-2891205">纪录的十个星期</a>。沃伦（Wallen） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallen-tells-fans-not-to-defend-him-over-video-of-him-using-racial-slur-2877773">说，他的举动感到“尴尬和遗憾”</a> ，并要求球迷不要捍卫他。</p><p>在此之前，田纳西州乡村明星在2020年10月违反了COVID-19-19的大流行指南，该指南<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/country-singer-morgan-wallen-pulled-from-snl-performance-after-partying-without-a-mask-2775511">在SNL取消了他计划的首次亮相</a>。两个月后，他确实继续在演出中演出，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/country-artist-morgan-wallen-jokes-breaking-covid-19-protocols-snl-sketch-2832956">开玩笑说在素描期间没有社交疏远的情况下开玩笑</a>。</p><p>自1月以来，沃伦（Wallen）一直在他即将发行的专辑（即将在5月16日发行）中戏弄和发行曲目。昨晚他还发行了两张专辑，他还发行了“超人”，“ Smile”和“我有点疯狂”。</p><p>人们认为，沃伦即将发行的专辑的名字是指近年来他的一些公共丑闻。除了2021年的丑闻外， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallen-arrested-for-throwing-a-chair-off-rooftop-bar-3614904">据报道，去年四月，这位歌手被指控犯有三项鲁ck危险罪和一项无序行为罪，该罪名</a>是在田纳西州的一家屋顶酒吧扔下椅子。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallen-abruptly-walks-off-snl-before-shows-end-3850420">摩根·沃伦（Morgan Wallen）的邮报突然走开了“ SNL”，然后演出结束时</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
